{"TopicId":161600,"ForumId":21,"TopicTitle":"Reliable Stock Colonies?","CreatedByName":"Casualnaut","CreatedById":178396,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-06-04T23:34:10Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Casualnaut","CreatedById":178396,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-06-04T23:34:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp style=\u0022margin-left:40px;\u0022\u003E\nSo in the somewhat future of my \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/161552-higher-paths-a-career-story/\u0026amp;do=findComment\u0026amp;comment=3079624\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EHigher Paths - A career story\u003C/a\u003E, I want to launch a colony to\u00A0so I can have\u00A0a \u003Cs\u003Edramatic disaster sequence\u00A0\u003C/s\u003E\u00A0nice way of earning science and money. I\u00A0want it to be nice for any sort of interplanetary travel, and also look\u00A0industrial;\u00A0so does anybody have some good advice on building one?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-06-04T23:34:35Z\u0022 title=\u002206/04/2017 11:34  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJune 4, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Casualnaut\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NSEP","CreatedById":165635,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-06-05T09:55:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI never built a colony. But make sure you have anything so it can self-sustain without frequent supplies all the time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Casualnaut","CreatedById":178396,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-06-05T15:07:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223080977\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022161600\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221496656542\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022165635\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022NSEP\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, NSEP said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI never built a colony. But make sure you have anything so it can self-sustain without frequent supplies all the time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell that is sort of the purpose of naming it a colony. A self supporting base really...\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NSEP","CreatedById":165635,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-06-05T15:18:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223081190\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022161600\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221496675259\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022178396\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Casualnaut\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 minutes ago, Casualnaut said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell that is sort of the purpose of naming it a colony. A self supporting base really...\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYup. And alot of space, for Kerbals/people to grow up in. I do not like spending my time in a puny capsule all day long. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Casualnaut","CreatedById":178396,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-06-05T15:19:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, I once made a sandbox colony of a MK 1 crew cabin and 3 ion drives. It was beautiful.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sardaukar11","CreatedById":78648,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-06-05T20:25:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni think roverdude has a mod for colonies, but i think its is more for surfac based colonies (they look more modular/square)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JadeOfMaar","CreatedById":167617,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-06-05T21:02:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223081506\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022161600\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221496694347\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002278648\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022sardaukar11\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n33 minutes ago, sardaukar11 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni think roverdude has a mod for colonies, but i think its is more for surfac based colonies (they look more modular/square)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere are parts for both orbital and surface colonies: the square-ish parts and just as many cylindrical parts. MKS used to be two separate mods, one for each situation, but they combined a long time ago.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-06-06T03:25:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis going to end up being a craft sharing thread, and so it has been moved to the craft sharing subforum.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KerikBalm","CreatedById":91917,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-06-06T23:04:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nif its stock, then ithere is no life support, everything is self sustaining... so just a bundle of hitchhikers, and maybe an \u003Cabbr title=\u0022In-Situ Resource Utilization\u0022\u003EISRU\u003C/abbr\u003E \u002B drills to supply fuel.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSoooo... here\u0027s a 100% stock 2 kerbal \u0022colony\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022JBM98Qi.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/JBM98Qi.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso 100% stock, maybe more what you\u0027re asking for:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022OENuo74.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/OENuo74.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00221aPSPuF.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022640\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/1aPSPuF.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022CpZQ8JO.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022640\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/CpZQ8JO.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nbut all the bases I\u0027m making now use the TAC life support mod and Kerbal Planetary Base Systems:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022jNCY8La.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/jNCY8La.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022nTX6baf.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/nTX6baf.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022NQaegvp.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/NQaegvp.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MiffedStarfish","CreatedById":175356,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-06-07T07:02:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt really depends what bodie you want to build it on. If it\u0027s on the Mun or minmus then you can muck about with Ion \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003ESSTO\u003C/abbr\u003E\u0027s, and generally focus more on aesthetics, while anything larger than Duna and you have to focus on ore mining to get anywhere near self sufficient fuel wise.\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}